Renee Torres https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Renee_Torres 0 Renee Torres (March 17, 1911 – December 27, 1998) born Renee Osterman, was a Mexican-American actress and the sister of Hollywood star Raquel Torres. A half-German half-Mexican woman,she appeared in a number of 1930s films, including The Devil on Horseback (1936), Captain Blood (1937), and God's Country and the Woman (1937).
